    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336990/extras/22c62c174f0972875a6e4d2d5da63953.avif?t=1750704072\" width=620 height=70 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336990/extras/651b02fa981813ad4d2c6b50f1034ddc.webp?t=1750704072\" width=620 height=62 /></span><br>玩家群：613685311<br><br>《开炮吧方舟》是一款融合了动作、建造、探索的生存肉鸽游戏。在游戏中你将驾驶仅存的陆上战舰，探索未知地图，营救船员，建造炮塔，升级战舰，打造属于你自己战斗风格的末日孤舰，纵横战场！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >无尽的敌潮</h2>魔法世界的变异萌怪还记得生前的技能，没事放个火球可不好办。对付不同的敌人偶尔转换下思维，有时候“逃跑也是战术”！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336990/extras/acd7660e49b430580b8c3a8cec5c755e.poster.avif?t=1750704072\" width=620 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336990/extras/acd7660e49b430580b8c3a8cec5c755e.webm?t=1750704072\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336990/extras/acd7660e49b430580b8c3a8cec5c755e.mp4?t=1750704072\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >炮塔：1+1&gt;2</h2>收集五花八门的炮塔，搭配组合再不断升级，巧思的放置在战舰的不同位置，谁说1+1不能远远大于2？<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336990/extras/34867f35d46fa55d8ce48f4766163c5f.poster.avif?t=1750704072\" width=620 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336990/extras/34867f35d46fa55d8ce48f4766163c5f.webm?t=1750704072\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336990/extras/34867f35d46fa55d8ce48f4766163c5f.mp4?t=1750704072\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你的陆上战舰</h2>想要纵横战场，就要不断升级强化战舰的各个部分和建造更多的炮塔，利用有限的资源创造你自己的战斗风格！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336990/extras/f746777799642739fe0294fd3e8da862.poster.avif?t=1750704072\" width=620 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336990/extras/f746777799642739fe0294fd3e8da862.webm?t=1750704072\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336990/extras/f746777799642739fe0294fd3e8da862.mp4?t=1750704072\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >别让厨师去打铁！</h2>营救或招募幸存者，扩大你的船员队伍，让他们做最擅长的事情，船员成长的效果也会有意外惊喜！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336990/extras/6cc77f853ea0d0228b910d5ad3758efe.poster.avif?t=1750704072\" width=620 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336990/extras/6cc77f853ea0d0228b910d5ad3758efe.webm?t=1750704072\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336990/extras/6cc77f853ea0d0228b910d5ad3758efe.mp4?t=1750704072\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索未知</h2>既然开船，哪怕是在陆地上，也要有大航海精神。各种未知宝藏，隐藏在萌怪汪洋之下等你去发掘。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336990/extras/550fe6c407f35fbdff69f120ab0301df.poster.avif?t=1750704072\" width=620 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336990/extras/550fe6c407f35fbdff69f120ab0301df.webm?t=1750704072\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2